#, php-format
msgid ""
"WARNING: This build step is new and experimental!\n"
"\n"
"To build **revisions** with CircleCI, they must:\n"
"\n"
"  - belong to a tracked repository;\n"
"  - the repository must have a Staging Area configured;\n"
"  - the Staging Area must be hosted on GitHub; and\n"
"  - you must configure the webhook described below.\n"
"\n"
"To build **commits** with CircleCI, they must:\n"
"\n"
"  - belong to a repository that is being imported from GitHub; and\n"
"  - you must configure the webhook described below.\n"
"\n"
"Webhook Configuration\n"
"=====================\n"
"\n"
"Add this webhook to your `circle.yml` file to make CircleCI report results\n"
"to Harbormaster. Until you install this hook, builds will hang waiting for\n"
"a response from CircleCI.\n"
"\n"
"```lang=yml\n"
"notify:\n"
"  webhooks:\n"
"    - url: %s\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Environment\n"
"===========\n"
"\n"
"These variables will be available in the build environment:\n"
"\n"
"| Variable | Description |\n"
"|----------|-------------|\n"
"| `HARBORMASTER_BUILD_TARGET_PHID` | PHID of the Build Target.\n"
"\n"
"EOTEXT"
msgstr ""
"WARNUNG: Dieser Build-Schritt ist neu und experimentell!\n"
"\n"
"Um **Revisionen** mit CircleCI zu bauen, müssen sie:\n"
"\n"
"  - zu einem verfolgten Repository gehören;\n"
"  - das Repository muss eine Staging-Area konfiguriert haben;\n"
"  - die Staging-Area muss auf GitHub gehostet sein; und\n"
"  - der unten beschriebene Webhook muss konfiguriert sein.\n"
"\n"
"Um **Commits** mit CircleCI zu bauen, müssen sie:\n"
"\n"
"  - zu einem Repository gehören, das von GitHub importiert wird; und\n"
"  - der unten beschriebene Webhook muss konfiguriert sein.\n"
"\n"
"Webhook-Konfiguration\n"
"=====================\n"
"\n"
"Diesen Webhook zur `circle.yml`-Datei hinzufügen, damit CircleCI Ergebnisse\n"
"an Harbormaster meldet. Bis dieser Hook installiert ist, hängen Builds und\n"
"warten auf eine Antwort von CircleCI.\n"
"\n"
"```lang=yml\n"
"notify:\n"
"  webhooks:\n"
"    - url: %s\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Umgebung\n"
"========\n"
"\n"
"Diese Variablen stehen in der Build-Umgebung zur Verfügung:\n"
"\n"
"| Variable | Beschreibung |\n"
"|----------|--------------|\n"
"| `HARBORMASTER_BUILD_TARGET_PHID` | PHID des Build-Ziels.\n"
"\n"
"EOTEXT"

